    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Meeting summarizer based on a transcript file\n\n## Use Case\nTransform meeting transcription into AI-friendly markdown format:\n- You need to process meeting transcripts for LLM analysis\n- You want to extract Meeting Title and Attendee's email from transcript\n- You need to send email to all the attendees with meeting summarize & key topics outline\n\n## What this Workflow Does\nThe workflow uses Open AI to summarize meeting transcripts:\n- Download the transcript file from Google Drive\n- Converts transcript to markdown format\n- Send email to all the attendees\n\n## Setup\n1. Create a [TimeOS.ai](https://www.TimeOS.ai/) account \n2. Add your Google Calendar to Sync with TimeOS\n3. Connect your Google Drive & Google Docs for transcript file to be uploaded after meeting is ended.\n4. Configure your preferred LLM connection\n\n\n## How to Adjust it to Your Needs\n- Customize output format for your specific use case\n\n",
        "height": 771,
        "width": 582,
        "color": 7
